> +            no-map;
> +        };
> +    };
> +
> +    dice {
> +        compatible = "google,open-dice";
> +        memory-region = <&dice_reserved>;

There's no need for this indirection. Just add the compatible to the 
dice@12340000 node. You can bind drivers to /reserved-memory nodes.

